Package: nonogram
Title: nonogram: Encoding, Solving, and Plotting Nonograms
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Hefin", "Rhys", , "hefin.r.rhys@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an S3 class for encoding nonograms (also known as Hanjie, 
    Paint by Numbers, Picross, and Griddlers), and methods for solving and 
    plotting them.
